(8, '<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="/flash_game/assets/flash_game/upload/images/featurebox_register.jpg" style="width: 137px; height: 77px;" /></p>\r\n', 'Lucky Lady’s Charm Deluxe11', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="a_4035" style="margin: -10px 10px 31px 3px; padding: 45px 0px 4px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-style: italic; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">\r\n	Lucky Lady&rsquo;s Charm&trade; Deluxe: Instructions</h3>\r\n<div class="container" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 11px 0px 15px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">\r\n	<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		At this slot machine or one-armed bandit game you must select the amount of Twists you would like to have available before the game begins. This amount will be displayed on the screen. You can use the +/- buttons to adjust your stake.&nbsp;<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		The &ldquo;Paytable&rdquo; button lists the win possibilities and the symbols. Simply press the green &ldquo;Start&rdquo; button to begin the game. Click the &ldquo;Autoplay&rdquo; button to spin automatically. Another click on this button will deactivate the function.&nbsp;<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<h3 style="margin: 38px -1px 31px -12px; padding: 0px 0px 4px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-style: italic; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 153, 204);">\r\n			Gamble:</h3>\r\n		<br />\r\n		The &ldquo;Gamble&rdquo; button will appear as soon as you have a win combination of at least two adjacent symbols from the left. In the &ldquo;Gamble Game&rdquo; you can double your Twists. Simply click the &ldquo;Gamble&rdquo; button and the game will begin. If you do not want to play the &ldquo;Gamble Game&rdquo;, you are free to carry on with the main game. You will be able to see the cards which you drew in the last &ldquo;Gamble Games&rdquo;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<h3 style="margin: 38px -1px 31px -12px; padding: 0px 0px 4px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-style: italic; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 153, 204);">\r\n			Free Game:</h3>\r\n		<br />\r\n		In a free game you can multiply your Twists. With a combination of three or more Crystal Balls anywhere on the screen, 15 free games will be activated. The stake used in the regular game will also be used in the free games. In the free games all of the winnings are trebled. Further information about the game can be found under &ldquo;Paytable&rdquo;.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">Be bewitched by the&nbsp;</span><b style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">&ldquo;Lucky Lady&rsquo;s Charm Deluxe&rdquo;</b><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">&nbsp;slot machine and increase your chances of winning. Ten paylines across five reels in the regular game, as well as numerous bonuses, will make you a winner.&nbsp;</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" />\r\n	<br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">The aim of the game is to achieve a line of 5 like symbols across the reels. In the regular game the win pattern starts at the first reel on the left and follows the payline across to the right. To win, the symbols must be adjacent (without any other symbols between them). The&nbsp;</span><b style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">&ldquo;Lucky Lady&rdquo;</b><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">&nbsp;symbol is a joker and it substitutes all of the other symbols, except for the scatter symbol (the Crystal Ball), and it doubles the Twists.</span></p>\r\n', '0', 6, '', 13, '', '', '', '', ''),
