e of football!&nbsp;<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			The objective of the game is to mow as much of the pitch as possible and therefore score the most points. The winner of the game is the player with the highest points total.&nbsp;<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			The game ends when the time limit is reached, or when the player has lost all of his/her lives. Each player starts with 3 lives. One life is lost if the player collides with one of the footballers. However, you may gain extra lives &ndash; see &ldquo;Points&rdquo;.&nbsp;<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			<strong style="font-style: inherit;">Points</strong><br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			For every patch of grass mown you are awarded 10 points. As long as you drive in the right direction, each patch increases in value by a further point.&nbsp;<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			But there are not only football players to be aware of - there are also devious moles intent on ruining your lovely pitch. Jump on a mole and score 100 points! Should you manage to land on more than one mole in a row, each mole will be worth an extra 100 points. Do this by jumping just before reaching the first mole and your second jump will be twice as far.&nbsp;<br />\r\n			<br />\r\n			A heart will appear after every second mole caught &ndash; collect hearts to get extra lives.&nbsp;<br />\r\n			While mowing, objects are thrown onto the pitch, such as</p>\r\n		<ul style="margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				Stars</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				Beer Bottles</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				Beer Cases</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				Toilet Paper</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				Flares</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '0', 5, '', 0, '', '', '', '', ''),
(32, '<p>\r\n	<img alt="" src="/flash_game/assets/flashgame/upload/images/11.jpg" style="width: 142px; height: 77px;" /></p>\r\n', 'Persian Treasures', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 id="a_3607" style="margin: -10px 10px 31px 3px; padding: 45px 0px 4px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-style: italic; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">\r\n	Persian Treasures: Instructions</h3>\r\n<div class="container" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 11px 0px 15px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">\r\n	<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			Persian Treasures is a puzzle game which is played by two players against each other. The players, however, need not play at the same time.</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			The playing field is covered by seven different types&nbsp;of&nbsp;precious stones. Each stone can be moved with a click of the mouse. The player receives 5 points for every stone removed from the playing field. Stones disappear from the playing field when three or more like stones form a row. The more stones a player removes at once, the more points he/she is awarded.</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			If a player becomes stuck during the game, not knowing where to make the next move, he/she can get help by clicking on the light bulb. A possible move will be highlighted, however every click on the light bulb costs the player valuable points.</p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px 0px 17px; padding: 0px;">\r\n			The stones may enter the playing field from any angle during the game. The direction changes every time the player removes four like stones at once. At the start of the game, the stones come from the top of the playing field. It is also possible for the stones to enter</p>\r\n		<ul style="margin: 1em 0px; padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px;">\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				from the right</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				from below</li>\r\n			<li style="margin: 0px 0px 0px -11px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 16px; list-style: outside; background-image: url(http://static2.greentube.com/xsl_gamebase/_gametwist_2010/imgs/bullet_gametwist.png); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; background-position: 0px 4px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;">\r\n				from the left.</li>\r\n		</ul>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The puzzle game&nbsp;<strong>Persian Treasures&nbsp;</strong>is played as a duel, meaning two players play against one another. However, the players need not play simultaneously.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The playing field is covered by seven different types of precious stones. The positions of adjacent stones can be switched with a click of the mouse. Stones disappear from the playing field when three or more like stones form a row either vertically or horizontally. The gaps left behind are filled by new stones, which can lead to chain reactions being set off.</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>\r\n	The game is over as soon as no further moves are possible or all of the stones have been cleared.</p>\r\n', 