(16, 'Rummy Tournament', '<p>\r\n	<span id="ctl00_UI_CPH_Content_UI_TC_Main_UI_TP_Details_UI_L_Description" style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px; display: inline-block; width: 600px;"><strong style="font-style: inherit;">It&#39;s all about honor and winning&nbsp;</strong><a href="http://www.gametwist.fr/help.asp?id_topic=27&amp;id_article=201" style="color: rgb(51, 153, 204);"><strong style="font-style: inherit;">Twists</strong></a><strong style="font-style: inherit;">:</strong></span><br />\r\n	<br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">1st Place: 15,000 Twists</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">2nd Place: 12,500 Twists</span><br style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;" />\r\n	<span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">3rd Place: 10,000 Twists</span></p>\r\n', 10, '2013-01-25 15:00:00', '2013-01-25 16:52:20', '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2px; font-size: 17px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-style: italic; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; border-bottom-color: rgb(51, 153, 204); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">\r\n	Brisca Tournament</h3>\r\n<div class="container" id="tournRules" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; overflow: hidden; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 16px;">\r\n	<p style="margin: 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px;">\r\n		<b>Participation</b><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		1. All platform players may participate in tournaments.<br />\r\n		2. Each player may only enter under one nickname.<br />\r\n		3. In participating&nbsp;in a tournament, a player gives his/her consent to the points detailed on this page and the rules set out in the&nbsp;<a href="http://www.gametwist.fr/display/page~agb/AGB.html" style="color: rgb(51, 153, 204);">General Terms and Conditions</a>.<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<b>Registration and Tournament Start</b><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		1. Each player must enter a valid e-mail address.<br />\r\n		2. Upon registering, each player receives the number of tournament points as stipulated by the tournament organiser (the platform). These points can be used in the tournament as stakes. If a player loses all of his/her tournament points, he/she cannot win any more.<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		<b>Order of Play</b><br />\r\n		<br />\r\n		1. For the duration of the tournament, players in the tournament room are regularly drawn against one another.<br />\r\n		2. Following a game, the points staked by the losing player go to the winner.<br />\r\n		3. Players who lose all of their points are knocked out and may no longer participate.<br />\r\n		4. If a player loses all of his/her points, the remaining games of the round are not played.<br />\r\n		5. If, after the stakes for the game have already been placed, one player does not finish the game, irrespective of whether this is voluntary, due to a loss of connection or any other technical problem, the &lsquo;ghost rule&rsquo; comes into force, meaning the computer takes the place of the departed player. If the computer wins, the game is not rated. A loss for the computer, however, is rated. Even if a player returns to the match, he/she cannot win, but may prevent the loss.&nbsp;<br />\r\n		6. The risk of technical problems